title: Official Nintendo SDKs (2010)
description:
This is the official development kits for Nintendo consoles that were available during 2010. All except for one are for game development.

The .rar file contains the following Nintendo SDKs:

Nitro SDK	- For Nintendo DS Game Development
RVL SDK		- For Wii/Revolution Game Development
TWL SDK		- For Nintendo DSi and Nintendo DS Game Development
